{"tid":1147758,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(中史科) 如何為聯軍帶路","createTime":"2019-05-10T04:41:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T06:06:16.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3f4996d2f0507a336829aad649d2d6c6a99ec857","tid":1147758,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T04:41:55.000Z","msg":"八國聯軍進京 老百姓紛紛&quot;帶路&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://m1.ablwang.com/uploadfile/2014/1120/20141120044030263.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm1.ablwang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2014%2F1120%2F20141120044030263.jpg&h=1a015e12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【圖1】1900年8月14日,八國聯軍攻打北京皇城，皇帝的子民們競相扶逃命。 當時的清兵和義和團兵不下20萬,大清和八國聯軍比例約10:1。 裝備上清兵一樣不缺，而八國聯軍的重武器還不如守城的清兵多。 然而清兵逃了個精光！ 留下了穿布衣長衫的百姓，也留下了這張真實的民眾競相扶梯相助八國聯軍的照片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://m1.ablwang.com/uploadfile/2014/1120/20141120044032540.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm1.ablwang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2014%2F1120%2F20141120044032540.jpg&h=00c8d3cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【圖2】這是一張珍藏在美國國家博物館（史密森尼博物院）的老照片，記載了八國聯軍1900年8月14日攻入北京城的歷史瞬間。 地點在廣渠門一帶，是北京外城城牆東側的唯一一座城門，此地屬於市郊。 聯軍正在順外城的下水道攻入城內，2個小時解決戰鬥&mdash;&mdash;可以肯定，爬下水道絕對有人帶路。 讓人驚訝的是，當他們爬上岸時，京城百姓居然齊齊站在河沿，作圍觀狀。 按照今天教科書上的解釋，八國聯軍打進京城，應該殺人放火無惡不作才是，京城百姓起碼應該和慈禧太后一樣四散逃亡躲避戰火。 然而我們從照片中，卻沒有看到百姓表現出怕的樣子，而是袖著手，抻著脖，平靜地圍觀，擺出一副與己無關的看熱鬧神態。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://m1.ablwang.com/uploadfile/2014/1120/20141120044034207.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm1.ablwang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2014%2F1120%2F20141120044034207.jpg&h=5d885ae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【圖3】1900年，八國聯軍攻占天津，獨輪車隊為聯軍把糧草送進城。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://m1.ablwang.com/uploadfile/2014/1120/20141120044036741.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm1.ablwang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2014%2F1120%2F20141120044036741.jpg&h=784e70ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【圖4】當地民船組成的運輸船隊通過白河往北京為八國聯軍運送物資。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.duping.net/XHC/show.php?bbs=10&amp;post=1321552\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.duping.net%2FXHC%2Fshow.php%3Fbbs%3D10%26post%3D1321552&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGnjL6x1fkqqvETpDxuWVMK8%3D&h=768286a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.duping.net/XHC/show.php?bbs=10&amp;post=1321552</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.xizhengw.com/UploadFiles/2015-05/282/201557143191799.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xizhengw.com%2FUploadFiles%2F2015-05%2F282%2F201557143191799.jpg&h=18aed3c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n百姓在幫聯軍過河<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.xizhengw.com/UploadFiles/2015-05/282/201557144596035.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xizhengw.com%2FUploadFiles%2F2015-05%2F282%2F201557144596035.jpg&h=b4bc82be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聯軍和小童合照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.xizhengw.com/UploadFiles/2015-05/282/201557153008022.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xizhengw.com%2FUploadFiles%2F2015-05%2F282%2F201557153008022.jpg&h=a7c44c48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.xizhengw.com/UploadFiles/2015-05/282/20155715220142.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xizhengw.com%2FUploadFiles%2F2015-05%2F282%2F20155715220142.jpg&h=dcebfc2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n百姓為聯軍扶梯子<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.xizhengw.com/3g/show.asp?m=1&amp;d=21120\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xizhengw.com%2F3g%2Fshow.asp%3Fm%3D1%26d%3D21120&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGnjL6x1fkqqvETpDxuWVMK8%3D&h=7a811ded\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.xizhengw.com/3g/show.asp?m=1&amp;d=21120</a>"},{"pid":"a6296c4a742eea27506db798daad48be3ead4f5d","tid":1147758,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T05:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1e1ed6514762bc0ed6fa0b716205cd6b232e8a","tid":1147758,"uid":225098,"like":1,"